local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["guerrilla"]={"guerrilla","[gə'rɪlə]","[gə'rɪlə]","n.游击队员",'n.游击队员|||adj.游击队的','A country of northwest Africa bordering on the Mediterranean Sea. Algeria gained its independence from France in1962 after a long terrorist and guerrilla campaign. Algiers is the capital and the largest city. Population, 16,948,000.','阿尔及利亚非洲西北部滨邻地中海的国家。经过长期的恐怖主义活动和游击战争, 阿尔及利亚于1962年脱离法国统治宣布独立。阿尔及尔是首都及最大的城市。人口16, 948, 000','He travelled on foot for several days until he safely reached a guerrilla base.','他徒步走了好几天, 最后安全到达一个游击队根据地。'}
